        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 3 at 2:54PM PDT by NWS Missoula MT</headline>
        <description>At 253 PM PDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Riggins, or 37 miles northwest of McCall, moving northeast at 30 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects.

Locations impacted include...
Riggins, Pollock, Riggins Hot Spring, and Lucile.
</description>
